I’m excited to celebrate the 10 year anniversary of BaldThoughts.com. I started out writing articles showing people how to use miles & points to travel, and it has evolved into something bigger than that. The lessons I’ve learned allowed me to quit the corporate world and write full-time while spending more time with my family. Thank you for all of the love & support over the last 10 years. I can’t wait to see what the next 10 years has in store as we continue to help people travel more, spend less, and live better.

Loving the views from our oceanfront junior suite at the @hyattzilaracanc. I’ve wanted to take Anna here for years, and we finally made it happen. 25k Hyatt points per night vs ~$600 cash. Excellent service throughout the resort and numerous tasty food choices at this all-inclusive resort. We splurged for the Chef’s Taste and the Tomahawk steak, and they were totally worth it. Highly recommend. #Hyatt #Zilara #Cancun #Globalist #HyattZilaraCancun #Mexico #Beach #BaldThoughts #WeTravelThere #instatravel

location.city_name: Metro Nashville Animal Care and Control

social_posts.post_text: We met Archimedes at @newheightsbrewing on Sunday, and my daughter instantly fell in love. We went to @nashanimalcare to pick him up for a #Pawdition. He loves to ride in cars and curled up in between our kids in the back seat. We take him on walks and he is so gentle that our 7yo can hold the leash. He’s calm with other dogs, but our cat is not a fan. Our poor kitty has been terrified, no matter how hard we tried to assimilate them. So, we’re returning Archimedes to the #Nashville Animal Control and trying to help them find him a forever home. Call (615) 862-7928 to learn more or visit 12p to 4p any day of the week. #adopt #adoptdontshop #adoptapet #nashvillepets #adoptadog #instahusky #instahuskies #huskies #huskiesofinstagram #huskylove #huskynation #nashvilletn #adoptionislove #adoptdontbuy #fosterdog #fosterhusky

social_posts.post_text: So many wonderful dogs & cats need your love & affection. Contact your local adoption agency to find your next pet. Decided to explore outside of Cincinnati and came across Milford, Ohio. It has an old-school, small town feel with a cute mix of old shops and modern renovations. Highly recommend stopping by Padrino for dinner. And there’s an ice cream shop next door.

We’ve learned so much this week at @getsharpsoccer in Cincy 🤩 I might be an overboard #soccerdad for taking the kids all over the US & Europe for their soccer education, but the skills & experiences are so worth it ⚽️ Plus, I’m always looking for excuses to travel ✈️ If you’re in the Cincinnati area, check out Andre’s #futsal & #soccer camps, group classes, and 1-on-1 training 💪 Highly recommend…except for the ants that kept trying to eat me and my iPad 🐜

Arrived in French Lick, Indiana, late last night 😴 Before heading out for a day of adventure, we stopped off at Nila’s Place 🥞 Big portions. Delicious food. Friendly service. And great prices 🤩 Thanks to Brandy for the recommendation @visitfrenchlickwestbaden #myfrenchlick #frenchlick #westbaden #indiana #frenchlickwestbaden #roadtrip #familytrip #summertime #breakfast #pancakes #biscuitsandgravy

The West Baden Hotel & Resort recently underwent a major renovation. It’s historic dome structure is awe-inspiring as you enter the atrium 🤩 When it was built, the free-standing dome was considered the 8th wonder of the world. Now, you can enjoy the views while having a meal at Ballard’s or from your interior balcony room if you’re staying at the resort. This is truly a special place. #myfrenchlick #frenchlick #westbaden #indiana #frenchlickwestbaden #westbadenresort #roadtrip #familytrip #summertime
Cabo is one our favorite places to visit. We try to go at least once a year. What’s your favorite beach getaway? #beach #familytravel #beachvibes #beachlife #beachgirl

When you @visitfrenchlickwestbaden make sure you stop by the German Café 🇩🇪 It’s such a cute building and the decor transports you to Deutschland for an authentic German meal 😋 The servers are so friendly and are dressed in Dirndls to complete the experience. They offer traditional German dishes like bratwuerste, goulasch, schnitzel and more. And save room for homemade desserts that rotate regularly 🍰 Learn more about French Lick West Baden on our podcast WeTravelThere.com/frenchlick 🎙️ #myfrenchlick #frenchlick #westbaden #indiana #frenchlickwestbaden #roadtrip #familytrip #summertime #foodie #instagood #foodinsta #yum #yummyfood

Our family LOVES water parks, and we had the opportunity to stay at @bigsplashadventure in French Lick, Indiana 🤩 While the water park is smaller than many standalone water parks, it wasn’t crowded and it was covered against rain & cold weather 🌞 We had a fabulous time in @visitfrenchlickwestbaden and can’t wait to come back! Learn more on our podcast interview with Brandy at WeTravelThere.com/frenchlick #myfrenchlick #frenchlick #westbaden #indiana #frenchlickwestbaden #roadtrip #familytrip #summertime #waterpark #hotels #sponsored

It was amazing to meet Andrew of @beverlyhighrye last night at the @1hotel.nashville and learn the story of his whiskey 🤩 We were invited to a special sneak preview of The Beverly Reserve, a limited edition barrel strength American whiskey 🥃 With a blend of 60% straight bourbon and 40% straight rye, you’ll experience rich layers of taste, including toasted marshmallow, caramel, candied pecans and a sensation of melted butter 😋 Aside from tasting the Reserve and High Rye, I also enjoyed a Spicy Southern Belle, which was delicious 🙌 The Reserve is limited to just 550 bottles and you’ll find it at select retailers, bars and restaurants in Tennessee, California and New York ✈️ Big thanks to @hjpr_agency & @travelmassivenashville for the invite to this exclusive event. #whiskey #whiskeylover #nashville #visitmusiccity #travelmassive #nashvilletn

We loved having the @eccosophy beach towels with us on our trip to Cabo ☀️ They pack light & thin, so they don’t take up much space 🙌 And they’re super soft & cozy, especially after you wash them 🥰 These towels are a great option when you want a splash of color or cool design at your pool, the resort or the beach 😎 #beach #towels #beachtowel #beachlife #summertime #travel #traveltips

I was invited to sample the new Beverly Reserve on the 19th floor at the @1hotel.nashville 🎸 This American style whiskey from @beverlyhighrye blends 60% straight bourbon and 40% straight rye for incredible flavor that melts in your mouth 🥃 It was also a fun opportunity to network with local hotels, bar managers, influencers and more 😎 #bourbon #whiskey #rye #beverlyreserve #nashville #tennessee #meetup #travelmassive #travemassivenashville #whiskeydrinker #bourbonwhiskey #bourbongram #whiskeygram #whiskeylover
